%20bots.%20These%20decoy%20pages%20don't%20affect%20search%20engine%20optimization%20and%20aren't%20indexed%20by%20search%20engines.%20They%20are%20specifically%20tailored%20to%20bots%2C%20which%20get%20ensnared%20in%20a%20meaningless%20loop%20of%20digital%20gibberish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20bots%20follow%20the%20maze%20deeper%2C%20they%20inadvertently%20reveal%20their%20behavior%2C%20allowing%20Cloudflare%20to%20fingerprint%20and%20catalog%20them.%20These%20data%20points%20feed%20directly%20into%20Cloudflare's%20evolving%20machine%20learning%20models%2C%20strengthening%20future%20detection%20for%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20Allen%2C%20VP%20of%20Product%20at%20Cloudflare%2C%20told%20me%20that%20more%20than%20800%2C000%20domains%20have%20fired%20up%20the%20company's%20general%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.cloudflare.com%2Fbots%2Fget-started%2Fbot-management%2F%23block-ai-bots%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Bot%20blocking%20tool%3C%2Fa%3E.%20AI%20Labyrinth%20is%20the%20next%20weapon%20to%20wield%20when%20sneaky%20AI%20companies%20get%20around%20blockers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloudflare%20hasn't%20released%20data%20on%20how%20many%20customers%20use%20AI%20Labyrinth%2C%20which%20suggests%20it's%20too%20early%20for%20major%20adoption.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20very%20new%2C%20so%20we%20haven't%20released%20that%20particular%20data%20point%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Allen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20him%20why%20AI%20bots%20are%20still%20so%20active%20if%20most%20of%20the%20internet's%20data%20has%20already%20been%20scraped%20for%20model%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNew%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20Allen%20replied.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20search%20for%20'what%20are%20the%20best%20restaurants%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C'%20showing%20high-quality%20content%20from%20the%20past%20week%20is%20much%20better%20than%20information%20from%20a%20year%20or%20two%20prior%20that%20might%20be%20out%20of%20date.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce3171f4-066c-4937-b985-95ffe6b072da%5C%22%3ETurning%20AI%20against%20itself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBots%20are%20not%20just%20scraping%20old%20blog%20posts%2C%20they're%20hungry%20for%20the%20freshest%20data%20to%20keep%20AI%20outputs%20relevant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECloudflare's%20strategy%20flips%20this%20demand%20on%20its%20head.%20Instead%20of%20serving%20up%20valuable%20new%20content%20to%20unauthorized%20scrapers%2C%20it%20offers%20them%20an%20endless%20buffet%20of%20synthetic%20articles%2C%20each%20more%20irrelevant%20than%20the%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20scrapers%20become%20more%20common%2C%20innovative%20defenses%20like%20AI%20Labyrinth%20are%20becoming%20essential.%20By%20turning%20AI%20against%20itself%2C%20Cloudflare%20has%20introduced%20a%20clever%20layer%20of%20defense%20that%20doesn't%20just%20block%20bad%20actors%20but%20exhausts%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20web%20admins%2C%20enabling%20AI%20Labyrinth%20is%20as%20easy%20as%20toggling%20a%20switch%20in%20the%20Cloudflare%20dashboard.%20It's%20a%20small%20step%20that%20could%20make%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20protecting%20original%20content%20from%20unauthorized%20exploitation%20in%20the%20age%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthwart-big-tech-ai-bots-feed-them-gibberish-cloudflare-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746106735000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6812c244c6ad288d147fa91f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthwart-big-tech-ai-bots-feed-them-gibberish-cloudflare-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20swarm%20of%20AI%20bots%20is%20making%20traffic%20surge%2C%20raising%20costs%20for%20website%20owners.%20If%20you%20can't%20block%20them%2C%20send%20them%20on%20a%20wild%20(digital)%20goose%20chase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%2