%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f6c1343fe8d39283629bde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Marine%20releases%20a%20drone%20while%20participating%20in%20the%20Super%20Squad%20Competition%20on%20Marine%20Corps%20Base%20Camp%20Lejeune%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3ELance%20Cpl.%20Abram%20Maestre%2C%20US%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20to%20field%20drones%20at%20scale%20in%20order%20to%20be%20able%20to%20pressurize%20our%20training%20really%2C%20to%20work%20through%20some%20of%20the%20real%20hard%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20Watson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20expects%20to%20see%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmore-than-a-rifle-marines-will-need-technology-in-future-wars-general-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarine%20Corps%20fielding%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20loitering%20munitions%20more%20broadly%20over%20the%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c406c9c-6056-4af3-90fd-5a4364f437b9%5C%22%3EThe%20'Valley%20of%20Death'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20seriously%20highlighted%20the%20value%20of%20employing%20small%20uncrewed%20aerial%20systems%20like%20quadcopter%20drones%20at%20scale%2C%20down%20to%20the%20squad%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20era%20of%20large%20fixed-wing%20drones%20like%20the%20Reaper%20dominating%20uncrewed%20warfare%20has%20ended%20as%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20drones%20surge%20onto%20the%20scene.%20Some%20military%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-special-operators-want-new-drones-for-dangerous-cave-missions-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrones%20can%20even%20fit%20in%20a%20backpack%20or%20pocket%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20coming%20around%2C%20but%20has%20been%20slow%20to%20adopt%20the%20tech%20widely%2C%20burdened%20by%20decades%20Global%20War%20on%20Terror-era%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26qu