26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20obstacle%20is%20one%20million%20percent%20cultural%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Col.%20Scott%20Cuomo%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20service's%20Weapons%20Training%20Battalion%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20Corp's%20new%20Attack%20Drone%20Team.%20The%20team%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20repository%20of%20knowledge%20to%20help%20boost%20drone%20usage%20throughout%20the%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECuomo%20spoke%20of%20a%20young%20enlisted%20Marine%20who%20used%20a%20%2420%20commercial%20simulator%20for%2020%20hours%2C%20and%20found%20a%20six-hour%20course%2C%20to%20develop%20drone%20proficiency.%20Such%20ad%20hoc%20training%20is%20a%20far%20cry%20from%20formal%20months-long%20certification-driven%20courses%20that%20the%20military%20uses%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20type%20of%20out-of-the-box%20thinking%20the%20Corps%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttempts%20to%20shift%20things%20up%20include%20newly%20established%20advisory%20boards%20to%20streamline%20communication%20from%20junior%20troops%20to%20Beltway-based%20colonels%2C%20but%20the%20Corps%20is%20poised%20to%20run%20up%20against%20problems%20not%20easily%20remedied%20in%20its%20quest%20to%20field%20more%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268e1a30c-a47e-45e4-9ce9-a2b30ea1ee0f%5C%22%3EA%20hard%20thing%20to%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Marine%20Corps%20is%20less%20agile%20financially%20than%20other%20services%2C%20a%20senior%20Marine%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Army%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-special-operations-forces-has-answer-to-militarys-weapons-problem-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpecial%20Operations%20Command%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20better%20equipped%20to%20quickly%20divert%20funding%20to%20new%20priorities%20like%20drone%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20Corps'%20money%20is%20heavily%20invested%20in%20its%20Force%20Design%20initiative%2C%20and%20those%20plans%20don't%20really%20include%20making%20