g%20my%20path%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cdf825e6-a937-4072-9e4c-6e4ce549225e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20moved%20to%20Spain%20as%20a%20student%20and%20never%20left%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20applied%20to%20teach%20English%20in%20Galicia%2C%20a%20northern%20region%20of%20Spain%2C%20through%20the%20Fulbright%20scholarship%2C%20a%20selective%20year-long%20program%20for%20students%20traveling%20abroad%20after%20I%20graduated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20rigorous%20application%20process%2C%20I%20was%20accepted%20and%20moved%20to%20La%20Coru%C3%B1a%2C%20a%20city%20at%20the%20northwest%20tip%20of%20Spain%20to%20teach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20my%20new%20position%2C%20I%20taught%20second%20through%20fifth%20grade%20English%20as%20a%20coteacher.%20A%20few%20weeks%20into%20the%20experience%2C%20I%20was%20already%20researching%20how%20to%20stay%20in%20Spain.%20I%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20amazing%20food%2C%20gorgeous%20country%2C%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20hustle%20culture%20compared%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20standing%20at%20a%20Fulbright%20awards%20ceremony%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681358baa466d2b74ab4b0ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKatie%20Passarello%20completed%20the%20Fulbright%20program%20teaching%20English%20in%20northern%20Spain.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Passarello%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Fulbright%20ended%2C%20I%20started%20working%20on%20my%20Master's%20in%20digital%20marketing%20and%20strategy%20at%20a%20Spanish%20university.%20During%20my%20studies%2C%20whenever%20I%20headed%20too%20far%20into%20overachiever%20land%2C%20other%20students%20in%20my%20group%20would%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20we%20can%20just%20do%20what%20the%20assignment%20says%20and%20not%20blow%20this%20out%20of%20proportion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20no%