%99s%20burdens%2C%20Smit%20would%20accompany%20him%20to%20the%20construction%20site%2C%20assisting%20with%20major%20lifting%20tasks.%20%E2%80%9CPappa%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20worry%2C%20I%20will%20do%20it%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20would%20reassure%20him%2C%20as%20they%20pulled%20and%20fitted%20massive%20iron%20structures%2C%20weighing%20100-500%20kilograms%2C%20onto%20towering%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20labour%20was%20not%20just%20physically%20taxing%20but%20emotionally%20wrenching.%20Yet%2C%20Smit%20was%20motivated%20by%20his%20desire%20to%20help%20his%20father%20avoid%20%3Cem%3Ekaali%20majduri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(menial%20labour)%20due%20to%20his%20health%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsmit-panchal-IAS-3-1745839908.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20At%20his%20home%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20once%20oppressive%20clang%20of%20metal%20beams%20has%20been%20replaced%20with%20the%20sound%20of%20dhols%2C%20garlands%2C%20and%20merriment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsmit-panchal-IAS-3-1745839908.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsmit-panchal-IAS-3-1745839908-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsmit-panchal-IAS-3-1745839908-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsmit-panchal-IAS-3-1745839908-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fsmit-panchal-IAS-3-1745839908-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-423548%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20At%20his%20home%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20the%20once%20oppressive%20clang%